  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And obviously-- actually, electrical engineering was-- was-- was the main and-- the main-- the reason, because-- because that factory was manufacturing all sorts-- all sort of electrical so-called switch boards, so-called fuse boards.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then they started to manufacture all sort of-- it-- it was called condensers, which is also-- we used it for a hundred different purposes.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the other part of the factory was plastic.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in those days, it was called Bakelite.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The word still exists, and Bakelite still exists.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Only plastic is-- is very different today to what it was at that time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were-- I was the oldest as far as the next generation was concerned in-- in the male line who could have taken-- who could take over.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Therefore, it was my destiny, planned destiny anyway, to-- to continue and take over.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I believe you enjoyed riding your bicycle and did little trips around your district.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Can you relate to us any time that you were harassed for-- for being identified as being a Jewish boy on a bicycle or any event?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, I can't say that I-- I did because at the time when I was riding the bicycle, [INAUDIBLE] [? it ?] [? could've been-- ?] it was over a long, long period, because we're talking from 1936, 1937 to 1943 maybe, right?",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And even after the war, one of my hobbies was bicycle.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I-- I really can't say, no.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No, I wasn't-- I wasn't attacked or any of the kind, no.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
